21
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:17,160
[The Legend of TAOTIE]

22
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:20,080
[Episode 21]

23
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:54,600
Qing,

24
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:56,880
get me the "so-called" Hibiscus Flame.

25
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,240
Mr. Lu,

26
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,750
this isn't for free.

27
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,720
You have to pay.

28
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,670
Or our accountant

29
00:03:15,670 --> 00:03:16,830
can hardly do his job.

30
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:50,440
How do you feel?

31
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,670
This bite is worth 50 liang, isn't it?

32
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,110
Why did you do this?

33
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,790
I'd like to help.

34
00:05:21,790 --> 00:05:22,350
Who?

35
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:25,920
Who's talking?

36
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,550
Miss Qu!

37
00:06:14,230 --> 00:06:15,670
Is that you?

38
00:06:19,110 --> 00:06:21,670
Someone told me
humans and demons couldn't be together

39
00:06:21,670 --> 00:06:22,880
and they would be far away.

40
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,760
I'd like to see

41
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:27,160
whether he'll fall to his death

42
00:06:27,350 --> 00:06:30,070
or have wings instead.

43
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,550
Miss Qu.

44
00:07:24,830 --> 00:07:25,480
Yan.

45
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:28,670
Yan.

46
00:07:42,270 --> 00:07:43,440
I feel so hot.

47
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:46,070
I'm burning to death.

48
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:47,920
I didn't know

49
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:52,390
I could see you before that.

50
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,160
I finally know

51
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:01,270
why those victims smiled when they died.

52
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,720
Because they saw someone

53
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,110
they hoped to see.

54
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:13,600
Yan,

55
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,000
I have something to tell you.

56
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:21,830
I'll never have another chance.

57
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:24,510
I...

58
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:26,830
If you leave now,

59
00:08:27,270 --> 00:08:28,350
you can live.

60
00:08:28,670 --> 00:08:30,230
No, no!

61
00:08:32,590 --> 00:08:33,470
I want to be with you

62
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,400
forever and ever.

63
00:08:53,110 --> 00:08:54,960
Yan!

64
00:08:57,030 --> 00:09:00,110
Yan!

65
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:12,960
Yan.

66
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,080
Yan.

67
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:55,470
Yan?

68
00:09:56,910 --> 00:09:57,910
Mr. Lu,

69
00:09:57,910 --> 00:10:00,000
you sound really intimate.

70
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,590
I guess you've seen a pretty girl

71
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,230
in your dream.

72
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:04,790
But in my restaurant,

73
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:06,230
there isn't a Miss Yan.

74
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:09,440
I saw her just now.

75
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:13,030
She shed a tear.

76
00:10:21,230 --> 00:10:21,880
Mr. Lu,

77
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:23,400
didn't you say

78
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,520
those who ate the Hibiscus Flame

79
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,760
would self-ignite and die?

80
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:26,840
But now,

81
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:30,320
you're still alive.

82
00:10:33,710 --> 00:10:35,230
I'll keep investigating.

83
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:37,030
If the dish didn't kill them,

84
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,520
I'll vindicate you.

85
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:42,550
The miracle of the dish is...

86
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:44,200
When you eat it,

87
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:48,030
you'll think of what you want to do

88
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:50,400
and see the person you yearn to see.

89
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:51,840
That's why so many people

90
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:55,400
are crazy about this dish.

91
00:10:55,710 --> 00:10:58,520
You must have felt it, huh?

92
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,840
This dish

93
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,550
is really extraordinary.

94
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,710
No wonder many people in Wuxia

95
00:11:08,230 --> 00:11:09,320
are obsessed with it.

96
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:10,670
So, Mr. Lu,

97
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,670
what did you see just now?

98
00:11:15,590 --> 00:11:16,520
I can't tell you.

99
00:11:18,470 --> 00:11:20,910
I'll take my leave.

100
00:11:23,590 --> 00:11:25,230
Remember to take Miss Yan back

101
00:11:26,110 --> 00:11:27,710
and ransom your bow.

102
00:11:31,150 --> 00:11:31,880
Bye.

103
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:33,280
Bye.

104
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,790
Mr. Lu, why do you stare me at like this?

105
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:57,150
I passed by the zither shop

106
00:11:57,750 --> 00:11:58,880
and remembered you said

107
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:00,240
your strings were loose.

108
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,150
I asked the shopkeeper to pick some.

109
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:03,360
Take a look.

110
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:04,590
Are they available?

111
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:10,800
Thank you.

112
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,190
The rouge

113
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,630
on your lips

114
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,040
looks so good.

115
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,320
You flatter me, Mr. Lu.

116
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:36,750
Qu...

117
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:40,440
Yan.

118
00:13:45,950 --> 00:13:46,750
These days,

119
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:49,590
I've never seen you smile.

120
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,270
I don't smile

121
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,040
or cry.

122
00:13:56,950 --> 00:13:57,510
Why?

123
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:01,320
Something happened to me years ago.

124
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:05,000
Since then, I've been disillusioned.

125
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:07,240
So, I don't smile

126
00:14:08,190 --> 00:14:08,950
or cry.

127
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:14,950
No wonder I can sense sorrow

128
00:14:15,830 --> 00:14:18,800
from your music.

129
00:14:21,920 --> 00:14:23,190
You never told me about this.

130
00:14:25,070 --> 00:14:26,920
Will you tell me

131
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:28,750
what makes you disillusioned?

132
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:32,560
It's been too long.

133
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:35,950
I can't remember.

134
00:14:37,190 --> 00:14:39,320
And it's meaningless

135
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:41,440
to bring up the old story.

136
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:44,320
Fine.

137
00:14:45,680 --> 00:14:46,750
Since you forget it,

138
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:48,270
I won't ask anymore.

139
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,390
I'm here to tell you something.

140
00:14:51,070 --> 00:14:52,560
When I investigated
the self-ignition case,

141
00:14:53,560 --> 00:14:55,510
I heard the new dish
in Tianxiang Restaurant

142
00:14:57,070 --> 00:14:58,070
could make people see

143
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,190
who they hoped to see.

144
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:05,120
You know what?

145
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,360
After I ate it,

146
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:09,880
I saw you

147
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,240
in my illusion.

148
00:15:17,830 --> 00:15:18,440
Yan,

149
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:22,480
I'm in my thirties.

150
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,390
It's the first time

151
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,710
I've cared so much for a lady.

152
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:30,190
So, I left Tianxiang Restaurant

153
00:15:30,830 --> 00:15:31,920
and came right to you.

154
00:15:33,190 --> 00:15:33,710
Yan, I...

155
00:15:33,710 --> 00:15:34,150
Mr. Lu,

156
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:36,750
say no more.

157
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:44,590
Am I so rash

158
00:15:45,270 --> 00:15:46,440
that you're scared?

159
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:49,270
Mr. Lu, you're an honorable archer.

160
00:15:50,190 --> 00:15:51,800
I'm a humble musician.

161
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:54,150
We don't belong in the same world.

162
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:55,710
How can we be together?

163
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,000
You and I have

164
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:01,190
different jobs.

165
00:16:02,590 --> 00:16:03,390
So what?

166
00:16:03,830 --> 00:16:05,150
I don't care about this.

167
00:16:07,040 --> 00:16:07,950
If you want to be with me,

168
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,880
I won't mind.

169
00:16:12,510 --> 00:16:13,480
You will.

170
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:17,360
When you know everything,

171
00:16:18,830 --> 00:16:19,680
you'll regret it.

172
00:16:19,680 --> 00:16:20,360
I don't mind.

173
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,630
I really don't, Yan.

174
00:16:22,950 --> 00:16:24,510
I thought about it on my way here.

175
00:16:25,150 --> 00:16:26,560
I know what I want.

176
00:16:27,070 --> 00:16:28,480
I don't know what happened to you.

177
00:16:28,950 --> 00:16:30,120
But what's gone is gone.

178
00:16:30,710 --> 00:16:32,510
I don't know what you suffered.

179
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:34,800
But I want to tell you.

180
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:36,320
From this day on,

181
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:38,510
you won't suffer anymore.

182
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:40,880
I will protect you.

183
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:45,360
As long as we have a future.

184
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:46,190
What do you say?

185
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:46,950
No.

186
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:50,710
We don't have a future.

187
00:16:51,830 --> 00:16:52,480
We don't.

188
00:16:56,830 --> 00:16:57,390
Why?

189
00:17:00,950 --> 00:17:01,710
I told you.

190
00:17:02,590 --> 00:17:04,110
I don't smile or cry.

191
00:17:05,230 --> 00:17:06,630
I'm dead inside.

192
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,750
I can no longer love anyone.

193
00:17:11,150 --> 00:17:11,750
Mr. Lu,

194
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,150
please leave.

195
00:17:21,080 --> 00:17:21,630
I'm sorry.

196
00:17:23,470 --> 00:17:25,040
Sorry to let you down.

197
00:18:04,230 --> 00:18:04,750
What...

198
00:18:21,470 --> 00:18:21,960
Mr. Lu.

199
00:18:25,870 --> 00:18:26,390
Mr. Lu.

200
00:18:28,110 --> 00:18:28,630
Mr. Lu.

201
00:18:38,870 --> 00:18:40,470
I ate the Hibiscus Flame
in Tianxiang Restaurant.

202
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:43,320
I really felt I was burning.

203
00:18:44,870 --> 00:18:45,390
But now,

204
00:18:45,390 --> 00:18:46,560
nothing is wrong with me.

205
00:18:48,750 --> 00:18:50,320
And people in that restaurant

206
00:18:51,230 --> 00:18:52,750
have no motive for the killings.

207
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:55,390
Mr. Shu,

208
00:18:55,990 --> 00:18:57,750
I asked you to investigate
the rosefinch's feather.

209
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:58,840
What have you got?

210
00:18:59,230 --> 00:19:00,350
I took my men to Market Dong

211
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:02,560
and interrogated the stall keepers.

212
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:03,750
So far,

213
00:19:04,150 --> 00:19:05,080
we haven't found

214
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:06,390
any clue about the feather.

215
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:10,750
Yundun,

216
00:19:11,750 --> 00:19:13,390
what have you got about Ge Liang?

217
00:19:13,560 --> 00:19:14,150
Mr. Lu,

218
00:19:14,600 --> 00:19:16,080
I found some important clues.

219
00:19:16,600 --> 00:19:18,470
Ge Liang is a merchant.

220
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:19,870
His family is clear.

221
00:19:20,230 --> 00:19:21,960
But Li Jiuzeng has many enemies.

222
00:19:22,630 --> 00:19:23,870
Ge Liang doesn't seem

223
00:19:23,870 --> 00:19:25,470
to be a Wuxia native, either.

224
00:19:25,920 --> 00:19:26,990
When he was little,

225
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:28,200
he moved in here.

226
00:19:28,840 --> 00:19:30,270
I went to his hometown
and asked his villagers.

227
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:31,990
But they said

228
00:19:32,630 --> 00:19:33,630
Ge Liang wasn't

229
00:19:33,870 --> 00:19:35,150
from their village.

230
00:19:35,510 --> 00:19:36,320
He seems as mysterious

231
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:39,390
as Li Jiuzeng.

232
00:19:40,350 --> 00:19:40,960
What?

233
00:19:42,390 --> 00:19:43,840
What a coincidence.

234
00:19:50,350 --> 00:19:50,870
This way.

235
00:19:52,510 --> 00:19:54,840
I deliberately picked this room.

236
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,230
It has the best view.

237
00:19:57,080 --> 00:19:58,720
It's quiet and elegant.

238
00:20:00,040 --> 00:20:01,110
Thank you, Miss Qu.

239
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,630
With you and the good wine in,

240
00:20:02,630 --> 00:20:04,080
I'm all right with any room.

241
00:20:04,320 --> 00:20:04,870
Please.

242
00:20:09,150 --> 00:20:10,870
It's the wine I made.

243
00:20:11,150 --> 00:20:12,040
I've kept it for years.

244
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:14,800
It's not sold on the market.

245
00:20:15,630 --> 00:20:17,920
Sadly, no one drinks it with me.

246
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:32,960
Miss Zhu, a toast to you.

247
00:20:33,870 --> 00:20:36,040
Thank you for helping me.

248
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:37,870
It's not a problem.

249
00:20:38,150 --> 00:20:39,600
You know I didn't help you for nothing.

250
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:41,270
Don't forget our promise.

251
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:41,800
Rest assured.

252
00:20:42,150 --> 00:20:43,840
I'll make my appointment.

253
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:55,750
Did Lu Ying come to you?

254
00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:01,510
He came and confessed his love.

255
00:21:01,990 --> 00:21:03,080
Did you accept him?

256
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:06,680
Why did you do that?

257
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:08,150
If I hadn't done that,

258
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:09,150
how would you know

259
00:21:09,150 --> 00:21:10,560
your real feelings?

260
00:21:13,270 --> 00:21:15,040
Stop match-making us.

261
00:21:15,630 --> 00:21:16,350
Why?

262
00:21:16,990 --> 00:21:18,720
Since you saved his life,

263
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:20,470
you must have feelings for him.

264
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:22,440
Why don't you try being with him?

265
00:21:25,390 --> 00:21:27,200
I used to think

266
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:28,680
I only loved my late husband.

267
00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:32,600
I didn't know I could love someone else.

268
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,080
I felt sorry for him.

269
00:21:36,350 --> 00:21:37,840
That was long ago.

270
00:21:37,990 --> 00:21:39,680
A dozen years have gone by.

271
00:21:39,750 --> 00:21:40,800
I don't think your husband

272
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:41,990
would want you

273
00:21:41,990 --> 00:21:42,920
to stay all alone

274
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:44,320
or live a lonely life.

275
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:46,470
He would want you to have a new life,

276
00:21:46,470 --> 00:21:46,960
right?

277
00:21:47,990 --> 00:21:49,150
You have a point.

278
00:21:50,150 --> 00:21:51,680
But I'm not brave enough

279
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:52,560
to take that step.

280
00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:57,750
Mr. Lu loves me now.

281
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:00,960
But it's because
he doesn't know the truth.

282
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:03,440
He hates demons.

283
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:06,040
When he knows, he'll regret it.

284
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:09,270
But if he knows what you suffered...

285
00:22:09,750 --> 00:22:10,390
Think about it.

286
00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:12,800
Will he still hate demons?

287
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:16,990
I don't know. Nor do I dare to think.

288
00:22:18,270 --> 00:22:19,470
Human nature is unpredictable.

289
00:22:20,630 --> 00:22:22,990
Even if he can accept my identity,

290
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:25,230
we have different lifespans.

291
00:22:25,840 --> 00:22:27,350
How can we stay together?

292
00:22:30,840 --> 00:22:32,510
You have different lifespans.

293
00:22:35,110 --> 00:22:36,840
How can you stay together?

294
00:22:43,630 --> 00:22:45,800
Are you thinking of someone?

295
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,920
I think you have a point.

296
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:53,720
I've never thought about it.

297
00:22:55,510 --> 00:22:56,870
I imagined it a million times.

298
00:22:58,200 --> 00:22:59,750
If only he hadn't died

299
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:01,080
in the battle 500 years ago!

300
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:04,440
If only he had stayed with me!

301
00:23:07,350 --> 00:23:08,720
But he was a human.

302
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:12,350
He would grow old and die.

303
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:14,990
I would still be left alone

304
00:23:14,990 --> 00:23:16,110
in this world,

305
00:23:17,560 --> 00:23:18,510
looking back.

306
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:25,750
So, Miss Zhu,

307
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:28,720
you also have a sad memory.

308
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:32,350
Don't mention it.

309
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:34,560
We should drink happily.

310
00:23:34,560 --> 00:23:37,110
Let's not think of anything so sad.

311
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:42,390
The wine

312
00:23:42,600 --> 00:23:44,840
tastes spicy and rich.

313
00:23:45,110 --> 00:23:46,990
Miss Qu, you make perfect wine.

314
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:49,230
Today, let's get drunk.

315
00:23:50,470 --> 00:23:50,960
All right.

316
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:52,440
Let's get drunk.

317
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:02,110
I'll drink as much as you want.

318
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:03,510
If you're drunk,

319
00:24:03,870 --> 00:24:05,270
stay here for some rest.

320
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,750
I can hold my liquor.

321
00:24:07,110 --> 00:24:08,200
I won't be drunk.

322
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:13,200
Cheers.

323
00:24:17,350 --> 00:24:19,200
Welcome, Your Highness.

324
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:20,680
Where's Miss Zhu
from Tianxiang Restaurant?

325
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:23,150
In the room upstairs.

326
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:25,230
Your Highness,

327
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:26,390
there you go.

328
00:24:44,630 --> 00:24:45,150
Your Highness.

329
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:47,560
You may rise.

330
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:49,800
Heng, what are you doing here?

331
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:51,510
I went to Tianxiang Restaurant for you

332
00:24:51,510 --> 00:24:52,110
but failed.

333
00:24:52,630 --> 00:24:53,720
They told me you were here.

334
00:24:54,840 --> 00:24:56,350
You're in a good mood, Miss Zhu.

335
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:58,600
Shall I drink with you?

336
00:24:58,720 --> 00:24:59,470
All right.

337
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:00,990
You're a chill guy,

338
00:25:00,990 --> 00:25:02,110
unlike Qing.

339
00:25:02,110 --> 00:25:03,800
He's always hesitant.

340
00:25:03,800 --> 00:25:04,600
He doesn't even drink.

341
00:25:05,560 --> 00:25:06,600
You enjoy the wine.

342
00:25:06,920 --> 00:25:08,200
I'll play some music for you.

343
00:25:08,990 --> 00:25:09,470
Sit, please.

344
00:25:10,040 --> 00:25:10,440
Sit.

345
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,080
Cheers.

346
00:25:58,320 --> 00:25:59,080
It's so late.

347
00:25:59,870 --> 00:26:01,040
Why isn't Miss Zhu back yet?

348
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:32,320
There you are.

349
00:26:38,080 --> 00:26:39,510
At last.

350
00:27:11,870 --> 00:27:12,600
Miss Zhu,

351
00:27:13,510 --> 00:27:15,110
