352
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:16,920
So are you.

353
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:20,040
Since you have feelings for him,

354
00:27:21,150 --> 00:27:22,800
why don't you have him?

355
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:25,270
Your Highness,

356
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:26,680
I have things to do.

357
00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:29,470
Please take care of Miss Zhu.

358
00:27:55,040 --> 00:27:55,510
Mr. Chang.

359
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:58,470
Cuiyan.

360
00:27:59,150 --> 00:28:00,990
The moon is so round.

361
00:28:01,510 --> 00:28:02,350
You're just in time.

362
00:28:02,350 --> 00:28:03,510
Go to Pingyue House.

363
00:28:03,510 --> 00:28:04,720
See what Miss Zhu is doing.

364
00:28:04,870 --> 00:28:05,440
Mr. Chang,

365
00:28:06,230 --> 00:28:07,470
why won't you go?

366
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:08,680
I think His Highness

367
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:10,680
went there for Miss Zhu.

368
00:28:10,990 --> 00:28:11,920
It's so late.

369
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:12,920
Don't you worry?

370
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,270
Come on.

371
00:28:18,800 --> 00:28:20,230
Go check on her.

372
00:28:25,630 --> 00:28:27,920
Miss Zhu, you're drunk.

373
00:28:34,230 --> 00:28:34,870
Miss Zhu.

374
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:36,600
Come on.

375
00:28:37,230 --> 00:28:38,040
I'll take you home.

376
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:39,680
- No.
- Come on.

377
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:45,390
Don't leave.

378
00:28:46,800 --> 00:28:47,600
You promised me

379
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:51,750
to travel around with me.

380
00:28:54,040 --> 00:28:55,390
But you left me all alone,

381
00:28:55,390 --> 00:28:56,510
keeping this promise

382
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:59,230
for so many years.

383
00:29:00,270 --> 00:29:01,040
All right.

384
00:29:01,990 --> 00:29:02,750
I give you my word.

385
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:04,680
I won't leave.

386
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:07,510
I'll always stay by your side.

387
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,390
Never leave me.

388
00:29:11,470 --> 00:29:12,440
I won't leave you.

389
00:29:14,990 --> 00:29:15,720
500 years.

390
00:29:18,270 --> 00:29:19,110
It's been 500 years.

391
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:21,270
I've been waiting for 500 years.

392
00:29:23,150 --> 00:29:24,440
Never leave me again.

393
00:29:29,150 --> 00:29:29,920
500 years?

394
00:29:34,350 --> 00:29:35,390
Who are you thinking of?

395
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:38,990
Come on, Miss Zhu.

396
00:29:39,990 --> 00:29:40,800
It's cold here.

397
00:29:41,270 --> 00:29:41,680
I'll move you up.

398
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:42,230
I'm not going.

399
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:42,750
Come on.

400
00:29:42,750 --> 00:29:43,440
I'm not going.

401
00:30:16,750 --> 00:30:17,840
I almost forget.

402
00:30:20,080 --> 00:30:21,680
I have no right to love you.

403
00:30:31,630 --> 00:30:32,630
With this body,

404
00:30:34,470 --> 00:30:36,720
I won't be loved, either.

405
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:44,440
Miss Zhu,

406
00:30:46,350 --> 00:30:47,840
when I look at you silently

407
00:30:49,110 --> 00:30:51,080
just like this,

408
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:54,630
I'm happy enough.

409
00:30:56,150 --> 00:30:57,840
I won't ask for more.

410
00:31:03,750 --> 00:31:04,870
I just hope

411
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:07,350
when you know what I am,

412
00:31:09,270 --> 00:31:10,630
you won't hate me

413
00:31:12,630 --> 00:31:13,510
or stay away from me

414
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:16,510
like anyone else.

415
00:31:23,510 --> 00:31:24,110
I just fear

416
00:31:24,110 --> 00:31:27,200
you won't stay with me anymore.

417
00:31:31,350 --> 00:31:31,960
500 years.

418
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,230
It's been 500 years.

419
00:31:46,040 --> 00:31:46,990
You seem

420
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:49,960
to think of me.

421
00:31:51,840 --> 00:31:53,320
Yet you seem not.

422
00:32:16,630 --> 00:32:17,200
Forget it.

423
00:32:19,230 --> 00:32:21,080
Even if you think of me,

424
00:32:23,800 --> 00:32:25,110
it won't make any difference.

425
00:32:37,630 --> 00:32:38,840
Hey, gentleman.

426
00:32:38,840 --> 00:32:40,150
Where's Miss Zhu
from Tianxiang Restaurant?

427
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,600
Oh, Miss Zhu.

428
00:32:41,600 --> 00:32:42,440
She and His Highness...

429
00:32:43,840 --> 00:32:44,560
Who are you?

430
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:46,560
The emperor.

431
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:34,080
Mr. Chang,

432
00:34:34,270 --> 00:34:35,120
what happened?

433
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:37,040
Now, she's wild.

434
00:34:37,400 --> 00:34:38,400
She got drunk,

435
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:39,360
slept in Pingyue House,

436
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:40,360
and didn't plan to come back.

437
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:44,600
Go get something to sober her up.

438
00:34:44,750 --> 00:34:45,200
Yes.

439
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:45,880
Hurry.

440
00:34:51,640 --> 00:34:57,000
[Pingyue House]

441
00:34:57,160 --> 00:34:58,360
What the heck!

442
00:34:58,990 --> 00:34:59,790
First, the prince...

443
00:35:00,360 --> 00:35:01,470
And then the emperor.

444
00:35:06,550 --> 00:35:07,160
Excuse me.

445
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:10,400
Who are you?

446
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,360
This is the Princess of Yunlong.

447
00:35:15,120 --> 00:35:15,920
Oh, Your Grace.

448
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:18,080
You must be here for His Highness.

449
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:19,790
He is upstairs.

450
00:35:22,230 --> 00:35:23,510
Here. Here are the stairs.

451
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:24,400
There they are.

452
00:35:25,840 --> 00:35:26,510
Be careful.

453
00:35:26,990 --> 00:35:27,920
Be very careful.

454
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:29,470
Slow down.

455
00:35:47,750 --> 00:35:48,270
Lian.

456
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,030
Oh.

457
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:01,710
You always keep me worried.

458
00:36:03,470 --> 00:36:04,790
You've been cultivating
for a thousand years.

459
00:36:05,710 --> 00:36:07,310
But you're still groggy

460
00:36:08,310 --> 00:36:09,160
and careless.

461
00:36:13,200 --> 00:36:14,270
I'm not being lazy lately.

462
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:17,470
I just want you to get used to it

463
00:36:17,470 --> 00:36:18,640
when I'm not around.

464
00:36:21,510 --> 00:36:22,790
When I'm away,

465
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:25,550
how will you live?

466
00:36:43,160 --> 00:36:44,360
Now, I finally realize

467
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:47,230
you stay here for Monk Lotus.

468
00:36:48,680 --> 00:36:51,200
Last time, you asked me
to take you up the mountain

469
00:36:51,990 --> 00:36:52,680
for the sunrise.

470
00:36:54,680 --> 00:36:56,710
You were so dedicated
when you watched it.

471
00:36:58,440 --> 00:36:59,470
I had never seen you

472
00:37:00,510 --> 00:37:01,710
behave like that.

473
00:37:09,160 --> 00:37:10,400
But now, how do you feel

474
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:11,510
about His Highness?

475
00:37:22,470 --> 00:37:24,030
One day, you said you thought it through

476
00:37:25,270 --> 00:37:26,640
and would have a new guy.

477
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:29,080
It must be him, huh?

478
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:35,640
I don't have much time left.

479
00:37:37,510 --> 00:37:38,440
I shouldn't have a fantasy.

480
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:42,950
Very well.

481
00:37:45,550 --> 00:37:46,600
He loves you.

482
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:49,270
Your love for each other

483
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:52,120
could be perfect.

484
00:37:54,030 --> 00:37:55,640
He will take care of you.

485
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:01,750
But since he loves you,

486
00:38:03,200 --> 00:38:04,600
he'll have a hard time.

487
00:38:14,750 --> 00:38:15,360
Miss Zhu,

488
00:38:20,120 --> 00:38:20,990
I don't want to leave you.

489
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:47,640
[Residence of the Prince of Langya]

490
00:38:57,880 --> 00:38:58,470
Your Highness,

491
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:00,310
since I came to Wuxia,

492
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:02,600
you've seldom stayed at home.

493
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:04,750
Staring at you like this

494
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,600
makes me happy.

495
00:39:09,230 --> 00:39:10,080
Sometimes,

496
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:12,710
I'm really jealous of Miss Zhu.

497
00:39:14,030 --> 00:39:15,510
When you stay with her,

498
00:39:16,270 --> 00:39:17,710
you remain true.

499
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:25,920
Miss Zhu,

500
00:39:26,710 --> 00:39:27,440
you know what?

501
00:39:30,270 --> 00:39:32,120
I'm a semi-demon.

502
00:39:34,270 --> 00:39:35,360
The humblest

503
00:39:36,510 --> 00:39:38,920
and lowest semi-demon.

504
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:43,440
My mother died at a young age.

505
00:39:44,400 --> 00:39:46,030
My father abandoned me, too.

506
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:47,990
I know.

507
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:51,710
Everyone despises me behind my back.

508
00:39:53,680 --> 00:39:55,310
I don't dare to tell you.

509
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:57,550
I fear when you know it,

510
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:59,270
you'll stay away from me.

511
00:40:06,640 --> 00:40:07,950
Now, you know it.

512
00:40:08,950 --> 00:40:10,310
Will you discard me

513
00:40:11,920 --> 00:40:13,160
as everybody else does?

514
00:40:16,550 --> 00:40:17,310
Don't worry.

515
00:40:17,790 --> 00:40:19,030
Whatever you are,

516
00:40:20,470 --> 00:40:22,200
I'll always be with you.

517
00:40:34,680 --> 00:40:36,200
Ge Liang and Li Jiuzeng

518
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:38,550
seem to be unrelated

519
00:40:38,550 --> 00:40:40,400
with nothing in common.

520
00:40:41,080 --> 00:40:43,080
But I think they're from the same place.

521
00:40:44,270 --> 00:40:46,200
They pretended
they didn't know each other.

522
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:49,030
I think they were hiding something.

523
00:40:58,200 --> 00:40:58,710
Mr. Lu,

524
00:40:59,310 --> 00:41:00,880
I found a strange village.

525
00:41:01,640 --> 00:41:02,400
There's only

526
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:04,750
a fire record about it 16 years ago.

527
00:41:05,200 --> 00:41:06,920
No more information.

528
00:41:07,790 --> 00:41:09,360
A village that disappeared.

529
00:41:10,790 --> 00:41:12,950
It accords with their background.

530
00:41:12,950 --> 00:41:13,790
What's the village's name?

531
00:41:15,550 --> 00:41:16,080
It's...

532
00:41:17,230 --> 00:41:17,920
Panyun Village.

533
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,400
Panyun Village?

534
00:41:44,710 --> 00:41:45,270
Qing.

535
00:41:47,120 --> 00:41:47,680
Qing.

536
00:41:48,600 --> 00:41:49,200
Qing.

537
00:41:50,640 --> 00:41:51,680
Instead of sleeping in your room,

538
00:41:51,920 --> 00:41:52,710
what are you doing here?

539
00:41:54,790 --> 00:41:55,440
You're awake.

540
00:42:02,400 --> 00:42:03,160
Come on.

541
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,120
Be more sensible, will you?

542
00:42:05,470 --> 00:42:06,750
Last night, I went
to Pingyue House for you.

543
00:42:07,200 --> 00:42:07,920
You and His Highness

544
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:11,640
lay in one room

545
00:42:11,640 --> 00:42:12,950
all alone.

546
00:42:14,790 --> 00:42:15,640
We did?

547
00:42:16,680 --> 00:42:17,790
I was excited last night.

548
00:42:17,790 --> 00:42:19,120
So, I was drunk.

549
00:42:19,310 --> 00:42:20,310
Why did you drink that much?

550
00:42:20,310 --> 00:42:21,440
Couldn't you restrain yourself?

551
00:42:22,640 --> 00:42:24,160
If I hadn't taken you back,

552
00:42:24,470 --> 00:42:26,120
who would know what he could do?

553
00:42:27,750 --> 00:42:28,470
Heng?

554
00:42:29,120 --> 00:42:30,400
He wouldn't dare to do anything.

555
00:42:30,750 --> 00:42:32,030
How do you know?

556
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:33,470
Even if you like him,

557
00:42:33,470 --> 00:42:35,030
do you know what kind of man he is?

558
00:42:37,230 --> 00:42:38,400
Who told you I liked him?

559
00:42:39,950 --> 00:42:40,710
Besides,

560
00:42:41,470 --> 00:42:43,470
I'm the owner of Tianxiang Restaurant.

561
00:42:43,470 --> 00:42:45,360
Don't interfere with so much.

562
00:42:47,200 --> 00:42:48,990
You're like a Miss Caring Boss.

563
00:42:48,990 --> 00:42:49,400
Oh, no.

564
00:42:49,750 --> 00:42:50,470
Mr. Caring Boss.

565
00:42:50,470 --> 00:42:51,790
I won't interfere with your stuff.

566
00:42:52,470 --> 00:42:53,920
You just always do silly things.

567
00:42:54,030 --> 00:42:54,470
No one

568
00:42:54,470 --> 00:42:55,880
can always keep you around.

569
00:42:56,950 --> 00:42:57,840
If you're drunk again,

570
00:42:58,080 --> 00:42:59,310
I won't go get you back.

571
00:43:00,440 --> 00:43:01,440
Anyone else can go.

572
00:43:04,440 --> 00:43:05,080
But last night,

573
00:43:05,600 --> 00:43:06,840
I didn't ask you to get me back.

574
00:43:10,440 --> 00:43:11,080
I just didn't

575
00:43:11,080 --> 00:43:12,680
want you to be fooled by a playboy.

576
00:43:13,270 --> 00:43:15,230
Or you'd lose a lot

577
00:43:15,230 --> 00:43:16,470
and even this restaurant.

578
00:43:16,750 --> 00:43:17,880
Then, where can I make money?

579
00:43:17,920 --> 00:43:19,080
Make money?

580
00:43:19,440 --> 00:43:21,710
You always think of making money.

581
00:43:21,950 --> 00:43:23,120
What do you need so much money for?

582
00:43:23,120 --> 00:43:24,120
For the dowry of your sister?

583
00:43:24,120 --> 00:43:24,470
I...

584
00:43:27,400 --> 00:43:27,790
Yes.

585
00:43:28,440 --> 00:43:29,270
I promised my sister.

586
00:43:29,270 --> 00:43:30,080
I'll keep my word.

