00:43:30,270 --> 00:43:31,550
Or how can I go home with money?

588
00:43:31,550 --> 00:43:32,470
Chang Qing,

589
00:43:33,080 --> 00:43:34,680
you've been slackening

590
00:43:34,920 --> 00:43:36,310
and taking less care of me.

591
00:43:36,550 --> 00:43:37,790
I should have docked your pay.

592
00:43:37,790 --> 00:43:38,950
You won't go home with money.

593
00:43:39,030 --> 00:43:40,270
Dock it. I don't care.

594
00:43:41,950 --> 00:43:42,600
Your temper

595
00:43:42,600 --> 00:43:43,950
has been worse.

596
00:43:44,840 --> 00:43:45,270
Get out.

597
00:43:46,470 --> 00:43:47,310
Get out now!

598
00:44:18,660 --> 00:44:24,390
♪Here's a flower for you♪

599
00:44:25,050 --> 00:44:29,530
♪I don't know what to say
when we look at each other♪

600
00:44:31,380 --> 00:44:37,170
♪Time goes by so quickly♪

601
00:44:37,520 --> 00:44:42,850
♪My obsession leads to my fate♪

602
00:44:43,350 --> 00:44:49,180
♪Destiny is confusing over the years♪

603
00:44:49,770 --> 00:44:55,710
♪It feels bleak even with the light on♪

604
00:44:56,050 --> 00:44:59,250
♪I see the shadow
when I almost forget you♪

605
00:44:59,250 --> 00:45:02,610
♪A ray of light on my journey♪

606
00:45:02,610 --> 00:45:08,800
♪It's like you're here
to pour out your heart♪

607
00:45:08,920 --> 00:45:14,940
♪Although the memories of our love
bring us pain♪

608
00:45:15,350 --> 00:45:21,510
♪All I ask for is to hold your hand
until the end of time♪

609
00:45:21,670 --> 00:45:24,820
♪Selflessly♪

610
00:45:24,980 --> 00:45:28,380
♪We taste the sorrows and joys♪

611
00:45:28,850 --> 00:45:35,860
♪I'll never let you go
till death do us part♪
